Okbaby Laguna Bath Tub (Blue) Price: Rs.1825

A baby bathtub will provide extra support to your baby’s delicate and wobbly body and help you in giving your child a safe bath. The Okbaby Laguna Bath Tub is described as a tub to grow up in as you can use this for your child between her ages of zero months to twelve months. This Laguna Bath Tub is made of polypropylene and has been carefully designed to last for a long time.

A thermometer is built into this bathtub that will enable you to keep a check on the water temperature that is used to bathe your bundle of joy. With the funnel and hose that comes along with this Laguna Bath Tub you can easily drain away the water and clean the tub after bathing your tiny tot. The drain plug in this Okbaby Bath Tub can be locked with the key provided with it which will curb your little one from unplugging the drain plug. Safety tested and TUV SUD Production Monitored

column16:
'desc': [u'

Okbaby Monkey Ergonomic Bath Support (Blue) Price: Rs.1195

Bath time with your newborn can be fun and a time to bond with them effectively. Making sure that your baby gets a safe and protected bathing experience is very important else there are chances that they can develop a fear for water. Okbaby’s Monkey Ergonomic Bath Support is a very useful bath accessory that helps you to give a safe and comfortable bath to your infant. The Okbaby Ergonomic Bath support has been contrived in a very practical shape that supports your baby’s wobbly body so that you can effortlessly bathe her. The three resting positions on the Okbaby keeps your little one securely in place without letting her slip off into the water.

Suction pads at the bottom of the Bath Support from Okbaby provides a firm grip to the Ergonomic Bath Support and keeps it fixed to one place till you have completed bathing your bundle of joy. With this feature you can affix the bath support even in the adult tub. Suitable for children from zero to eight months of age this Bath Support from Okbaby can support a maximum of 8 kg and it has dimensions of 31 x 23 x 66 cm.

column16:
'desc': [u'

Okbaby Onda The Smart Tub (Orange) Price: Rs.2495

Bathing your infant can be a lot easier with a bathtub as it will give extra support to your baby’s wobbly body. The Okbaby Onda Bath Tub has been anatomically designed so that it fits your bundle of joy’s body perfectly. With a three point support system that gives specific support under the armpits and between the legs so that you get to bathe your child with utmost care and ease. This Onda Baby Bath Tub can be used for children from the age of zero to twelve months.

This Okbaby the Smart Tub has a built-in thermometer that will aid in keeping a check on the temperature of the water in the tub. With the supporting bars that expand you will be able to fit in the Onda Bath Tub to your bath tub effortlessly. After bathing your tiny tot you can easily clean this Bath Tub using the hose and funnel that will drain the water. The drain plug in this Smart Tub comes with a key with which you can lock the drain and prevent your little on opening it. This Baby Bath tub from Okbaby that has the dimensions of 53 x 26 x 93 cm can support a maximum weight of 10 kg.
